  <brief_title>Capsule Endoscopy vs Standard of Care for Obscure Intestinal Bleeding</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Randomized Controlled Trial of Capsule Endoscopy vs Standard Care in Patients With Iron Deficiency Anemia With Suspected Obscure / Occult Gastrointestinal Bleeding</official_title>
